{
  "texts": [
    "This allows synergies to emerge and diverse forms of memory storage to exist.",
    "The energy to produce information is expended in searching details and changes in the structure of physical entities and encoding them.",
    "Whereas the energy produced by these changes depends on the energies stored or controlled by the system.",
    "No direct proportionality between both exists.",
    "A single click on a button can release the energy of an atomic bomb."
  ]
